profile_positions.description:
Liaised with distributors/direct clients, in-house and remote sales teams to define, develop and implement project requirements, scope, and objectives;
Kept track of orders status by coordinating with the Logistics Controller, handling Purchase Order, Stock, Shipping Documents, and Delivery Control;
Organized samples and catalogs requested by customers and distributors;
Provided quotations for projects, processed, and co-ordinated sales inquiries, liaising with Europe and Tokyo office;
Addressed customer inquiries and advised on products through the website, email, and telephone;
Performed proactive telephone sales campaigns.

Translated and reviewed emails, documents and ministerial permits in FR, EN, SP
Executed Sales Plan for Wholesale/Tenders for key and standard B2B and B2C customers, including UNDP, Partners in Health, local Ministries of Health, central buying services, Universities and research centers;
Drew up quotes and managed complex sales orders, from proposal to delivery follow up, assisting with Customs, Waivers, Licenses and Ministerial permits;
Performed exceptional pre-sales/after-sales activities, including identifying new business, cross selling, and outbound sales calls (VC) and emails;
Delivered responsive customer service by keeping into contact during the execution of the sales plan and confirming specific service requirements for Key-accounts;
Proactively generated, analyzed and followed up on customer satisfaction data to identify and implement improvements;
Actively participating in internal communication group meetings with the goal of improving IDA interdepartmental communication.
Interpreted in Trade Shows, HR events and clients
Performed cross-platform language verification tests from CRM Platform Navision to JDEdwards to

Ensured the highest levels of customer service towards ECCO's customers within the French and Italian markets;
Professionally managed B2B and B2C customers' orders, providing exceptional communication in areas of daily activities to the customers, sales team and HQ;
Handled all issues from order intake to order flow and run business reports on a daily/monthly/quarterly/yearly basis, in order to maximize sales activities;
Responded promptly to customer inquiries in person or via the phone, letter, email and social medias always in a professional and efficient manner;   
Proactively involved in marketing campaigns, event plans, social media evaluation,  content edition and translation;
Assisted customers during Salesforce Partner site 2.0 project launch phase supporting the related departments through improvement feedback and testing;
Represented ECCO in international Sales Events.

Ensured timely floor setup, marketing campaigns, coordination of commercial events and seasonal business activities, such as international B2B and B2C tradeshows and function events within Europe; Closed new business and developed negotiating strategies by coordinating prospects goals and requirements with company objectives and procedures; 
Built, maintained and nourished long term relationships with clients, planning and organizing work schedule to manage the daily orders and general operations; Marketed company products and services to current clients and prospects in international B2B and B2C partnership events and tradeshows in Europe; 
Reviewed business performance, innovated budgets and forecasts and provided consultation to key clients to ensure attainment of strategic sales goals; 
Proactively communicated with clients to determine their problems and account handling needs, keeping records of customer interactions and transactions, recording details of inquiries, complaints, comments, and actions taken; 
Translated project proposals, marketing materials, and business correspondence

Managed customer relationship and orders, handled customer inquiries and complaints;
Acquired new accounts and strengthening business relationships through international B2B and B2C tradeshows, cold-calling and marketing campaigns;
Provided professional translation and interpretation service for project proposals and business communication needs.
